  "names": [
    {
      "full_name": "“State Unitary Enterprise of the Crimean Republic ‘Crimean Sea Ports’”",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "The “Parliament of Crimea” adopted Resolution No 1757-6/14 on 17 March 2014“On nationalisation of some companies belonging to the Ukrainian Ministries of Infrastructure or Agriculture” and Resolution No 1865-6/14 on 26 March 2014“On State-Owned Enterprise ‘Crimean Sea Ports’” (“О Государственном предприятии ‘Крымские морские порты’”) declaring the appropriation of assets belonging to several State enterprises which were merged into the “State Unitary Enterprise of the Crimean Republic ‘Crimean Sea Ports’” on behalf of the “Republic of Crimea”. Those enterprises were thus effectively confiscated by the Crimean “authorities” and the “Crimean Sea Ports” has benefited from the illegal transfer of their ownership.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}